Name: How, with tools?
Subhead: epubbery

A ruby gem written by Jason LaPier (that's me). 

* https://github.com/jlapier/epubbery (or install with rubygems)
* designed to work like a web framework - you start a new project and get a template structure that is used to generate the EPUB
* no ruby coding required: templates are written in liquid, text is textile markup
* used to build this presentation